f: X \rightarrow X \times X
f(x) = (x,x).
df_x(v) = (v,v).
\begin{eqnarray*} df_x(v) &=& \lim_{t \rightarrow 0} \frac{f(x + tv) - f(x)}{t}\\ & = & \lim_{t \rightarrow 0} \frac{(x+tv, x+tv) - (x,x)}{t}\\ & = & \lim_{t \rightarrow 0} \frac{(tv,tv)}{t}\\ & = & \lim_{t \rightarrow 0} (v,v)\\ & = & (v,v). \end{eqnarray*}
